1. It's important to differentiate between refugees and tourists. Refugees are people fleeing from danger and seeking safety, while tourists are people traveling for leisure.2. The fact that some refugees may have entered Spain without proper registration does not mean that all of them are doing so.3. It is the responsibility of the Spanish authorities to manage the situation and ensure the safety of both the refugees and the tourists.4. It is important to remember that the vast majority of refugees are peaceful people who just want to live in safety and contribute to their new communities.5. Let's focus on finding solutions rather than spreading fear and hate.
